cast.overview: Slevin is mistakenly put in the middle of a personal war between the city’s biggest criminal bosses. Under constant watch, Slevin must try not to get killed by an infamous assassin and come up with an idea of how to get out of his current dilemma.
cast.title: Lucky Number Slevin

details.biography:
Jennifer Miller is a Canadian actress, best known for her role as the telekinetic, Alex in 5ive Girls. She has also starred in many teen dramas including The Best Years and Radio Free Roscoe.
